properties.headline: Freeze Warning issued January 20 at 2:55AM EST until January 21 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Tampa Bay Ruskin FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...28 to 32 degrees Tuesday morning. 25 to 29 degrees
Wednesday morning.

* WHERE...Coastal Levy and Inland Levy Counties.

* WHEN...For the Freeze Warning, from 3 AM to 9 AM EST Tuesday.
For the Freeze Watch, from late Tuesday night through
Wednesday morning.

* IMPACTS...Frost and freeze conditions will kill crops and other
sensitive vegetation. Remember to bring pets indoors.
properties.instruction:
A Freeze Warning means sub-freezing temperatures are imminent or
highly likely. These conditions will kill crops and other
sensitive vegetation.
